(N1064R1)1859 3065 MS
[38 0 0 -38 0 0]/Times-Roman MF
(There are at least 41 signatures affected.  Because some of these include multiple defaults, there are a total)521 261 MS
(of 54 cases.)521 306 MS
(An additional signature would have to be added to the library to deal with each of the cases, a total of 54)521 396 MS
(new signatures in all.)521 441 MS
(Of the 41 signatures affected, 29 are constructors.  Because the classes involved already have several)521 531 MS
(constructors, adding additional constructors is particularly confusing.  The use of default arguments makes)521 576 MS
(these classes easier to understand and easier to use.)521 621 MS
(Proposed Resolution:)221 711 MS
(Default arguments for member functions of template classes should either be added to the language or)521 756 MS
(removed from the library.  The "Plum Patch" is not intended to be a permanent solution to the problem.)521 801 MS
(The core working group continues to investigate a language change while the library working group)521 846 MS
(continues to investigate library changes.)521 891 MS
