[37.996 0 0 -37.996 0 0]/Symbol MF
(\267)671 1609 MS ( )688 1609 MS
[38 0 0 -38 0 0]/Times-Roman MF
(adding complex macros to headers to avoid nested namespaces.)730 1609 MS
[37.996 0 0 -37.996 0 0]/Symbol MF
(\267)671 1656 MS ( )688 1656 MS
[38 0 0 -38 0 0]/Times-Roman MF
(ensuring that names are consistently available \(or not\) in namespace std regardless of the)730 1656 MS
(order of header file inclusion in a user program.)730 1701 MS
[37.996 0 0 -37.996 0 0]/Symbol MF
(\267)671 1748 MS ( )688 1748 MS
[38 0 0 -38 0 0]/Times-Roman MF
(coordinating an effort to modify, rewrite, reorganize C headers supplied by a C development)730 1748 MS
